---
title: Thai Coconut Curry Shrimp with Bell Pepper and Cilantro Lime Rice
description: Think a restaurant-worthy curry is out of your homemade dinner grasp? Think again. Here, chicken thighs and bell pepper strips are seared until browned, then simmered in a creamy, dreamy coconut milk curry with Thai chili sauce and lime juice. Once the curry is thickened, and the veggies are tender, spoon everything over fluffy cilantro-lime rice and sprinkle with fresh cilantro and chili flakes. All that in just 30 minutes—talk about game-changing dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/663a6e88be3ee05a950c3887-4f988f86.jpeg
